    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i really feel like my sugar is spiking cuz i feel so lightheaded and dizzy. i can't wait to find my meter, i feel like i need to do something right now so i don't pass out from high sugar. if i just take 2 units of rapid acting it won't hurt much right? it's better to be safe and lower it a bit than to let it stay high and dangerous.",
